  "body": "<!--NOTE:\r\n- General questions should go to the discord chat instead of the issue tracker.\r\n-->\r\nHi,\r\nFor CI/CD needs we run a private ETH network that is tuned to speed up network\r\nIt doesn't match minimal preset and, sadly, there's no built-in way to customize it or override completely, for now we've used a hacky solution but moving forward would love to have an option to do it in lodestar.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nI'd like to come forward with a PR that adds an ability to use custom preset for chain config, but before starting working on it, would like to confirm with your team that it's something that you'd be willing to accept\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered**\r\nThere's no way to override preset variables in the runtime, so as of now we directly modify them in the source code during build stage.\r\n\r\n",
