    "body": "Hey @daniildxb  This is definitely something we'd be willing to accept.\r\n\r\nTake a look at https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/unstable/packages/params/src/setPreset.ts\r\nThis is my thought at what you could add:\r\n```ts\r\nexport let userOverrides: Partial<BeaconPreset> | null = null;\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * @param presetName - the preset to use as a base\r\n * @param overrides - customized fields\r\n */\r\nfunction setCustomPreset(presetName: PresetName, overrides: Partial<BeaconPreset>): void {\r\n  setActivePreset(presetName);\r\n  userOverrides = overrides;\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nAnd then [here](https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/unstable/packages/params/src/index.ts#L86) spread `userOverrides` in.",
